1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:05,200
Science has a clearer story about case reports limits than social media does.

2
00:00:05,200 --> 00:00:06,800
Case reports are anecdotal.

3
00:00:06,800 --> 00:00:08,800
They tell a single story.

4
00:00:08,800 --> 00:00:11,600
But can we generalize from one patient?

5
00:00:11,600 --> 00:00:13,600
What if it misleads us?

6
00:00:13,600 --> 00:00:16,400
Research shows case reports lack rigorous testing.

7
00:00:16,400 --> 00:00:18,000
They can exaggerate outcomes.

8
00:00:18,000 --> 00:00:21,600
Relying solely on them can lead to dangerous decisions.

9
00:00:21,600 --> 00:00:24,400
Stay informed, trust science, and think critically.

10
00:00:24,400 --> 00:00:26,000
Follow for more insights!
